        <div class="slide-quote heading-anim slide-quote">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque vehicula sapien vel urna malesuada fringilla et consequat dignissim.
        </div>
        
        <div class="slide-deco"><div class="slide-deco-mark">✦</div></div>
        
        {/* 2. PARAGRAF BAWAH (PERBAIKAN): Kita ganti kelasnya jadi about-text-fade biar tanda petik bawahnya HILANG TOTAL, 
            dan kita kasih inline style lebar 100% biar teksnya langsung plong melebar gak kegencet lagi */}
        <p class="slide-body heading-anim about-text-fade" style="width: 100% !important; max-width: 850px !important; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important; padding: 0 !important; text-align: center !important;">
          Curabitur luctus felis ac nunc venenatis, vitae sodales purus ultrices. Integer convallis magna nec lacus consequat, vel vestibulum nisl accumsan. Vivamus sagittis ante a felis dignissim, ut luctus odio fermentum sed euismod tortor vel nunc pretium.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slide" id="slide-2">
      <div class="slide-section-label">Roadmap</div>
      <h3 class="roadmap-title heading-anim">Where I'm Heading</h3>
      {/* SUNTIK STAGGERED: Node roadmap diberi delay berurutan biar naik satu per satu dengan indah */}
      <div class="roadmap">
        <div class="roadmap-node" data-delay="0"><div class="roadmap-dot active-dot"></div><div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 01 — Now</div><div class="roadmap-label">Foundation</div><div class="roadmap-desc">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit quisque vehicula sapien.</div></div>
        <div class="roadmap-node" data-delay="150"><div class="roadmap-dot"></div><div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 02 — 2026</div><div class="roadmap-label">Expansion</div><div class="roadmap-desc">Curabitur luctus felis ac nunc venenatis vitae sodales purus ultrices.</div></div>
        <div class="roadmap-node" data-delay="300"><div class="roadmap-dot"></div><div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 03 — 2027</div><div class="roadmap-label">Building</div><div class="roadmap-desc">Integer convallis magna nec lacus consequat vel vestibulum nisl acc.</div></div>
        <div class="roadmap-node" data-delay="450"><div class="roadmap-dot"></div><div class="roadmap-phase">Phase 04 — 2028+</div><div class="roadmap-label">Launch</div><div class="roadmap-desc">Vivamus sagittis ante a felis dignissim ut luctus odio fermentum.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slider-controls">
      <div class="slider-dot active" data-slide="0"></div>
      <div class="slider-dot" data-slide="1"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider"><div class="section-divider-diamond"></div></div>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq-section" class="has-corners corner-bottom">
  <div class="faq-inner">
