  <div class="contact-eyebrow fade-in">Let's Connect</div>
  <h2 class="contact-heading heading-anim">ini nanti<br><em>kontak sih.</em></h2>
  
  <p class="contact-para heading-anim about-text-fade">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque vehicula sapien vel urna malesuada fringilla dignissim et consequat. Curabitur luctus felis nunc venenatis vitae sodales.</p>
  
  <div class="contact-deco fade-in"><div class="contact-deco-line"></div><div class="contact-deco-mark">◆</div><div class="contact-deco-line"></div></div>
  <a href="#" class="contact-btn fade-in">Open Links <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M7 1l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></a>
